Package: FlyDeconv
Title: Cell-Type Deconvolution for Multiple Drosophila Tissues
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Jing",
           family = "Sun",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "your_email@example.com")
Description: FlyDeconv is an R package for cell-type deconvolution analysis
    across multiple Drosophila tissues. It provides a unified interface for
    running multiple deconvolution methods, together with built-in reference
    data resources for Drosophila bulk and single-cell transcriptomic analysis.
